title: Severe Power Outages EDA & Prediction Model

title: Geolocational Dinosaur Findings Data Visualizer
description: A data visualization mapping out carnivorous dinosaur fossil findings to answer the question: How likely are you to be eaten by a dinosaur right now?

title: N-Gram Language Model
description: A language model built using conditional probability of word sequences to generate coherent and meaningful text.
